[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71301, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9694, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 296629, "username": "huluwa561", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/huluwa561", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9037/1692/296629_mini.png?m=1780132248", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9037/1692/296629_normal.png?m=1780132248", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9037/1692/296629_large.png?m=1780132248", "created": 1520216610, "last_modified": 1780132248, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "eastvipcn", "last_touched": 1780169754, "title": "大佬们 vibe coding 的项目怎么样了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216679", "created": 1780132665, "deleted": 0, "content": "![image]( https://img.nodebits.xyz/i/2026/05/30/sa3wrc.png)\r\n![image]( https://img.nodebits.xyz/i/2026/05/30/sarbgt.png)\r\n从 4 月 16 日到今天（ 2026 年 5 月 30 日），一共是 44 天\r\n\r\n以上是我 vibe coding 的访问量\r\n\r\n大佬们的怎么样了\r\n\r\n欢迎分享，学习，交流\r\n\r\n地址在这：[nodebits]( https://www.nodebits.xyz/)", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://img.nodebits.xyz/i/2026/05/30/sa3wrc.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"image\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://img.nodebits.xyz/i/2026/05/30/sarbgt.png\"/>\n从 4 月 16 日到今天（ 2026 年 5 月 30 日），一共是 44 天</p>\n<p>以上是我 vibe coding 的访问量</p>\n<p>大佬们的怎么样了</p>\n<p>欢迎分享，学习，交流</p>\n<p>地址在这：<a href=\"https://www.nodebits.xyz/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nodebits</a></p>\n", "last_modified": 1780132665, "replies": 44, "id": 1216679}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_large.png?m=1751736790", "name": "claude", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_normal.png?m=1751736790", "title": "Claude", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/claude", "topics": 566, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Claude", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_mini.png?m=1751736790", "stars": 548, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1148, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 613803, "username": "GG5332", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/GG5332", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c67f1f43da09b5712741c7420913ea03?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c67f1f43da09b5712741c7420913ea03?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c67f1f43da09b5712741c7420913ea03?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1676258011, "last_modified": 1732159034, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "shuiandy", "last_touched": 1780176753, "title": "有大佬用上了 Claude Mythos Preview 吗？感觉挖洞是下一个被颠覆的工作了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216615", "created": 1780106530, "deleted": 0, "content": "Anthopic 四月发了博文说搞了一个 Claude Mythos Preview ，挖了 500+个漏洞，前几天又更新了进展，扫描了 1000 多个开源项目发现了估计为 23019 个漏洞，某家独立的安全研究公司对其中 1752 个高危或严重级别漏洞进行了仔细评估，其中 90.6%（ 1587 个）被证实为有效漏洞，62.4%（ 1094 个）被确认为高危或严重级别。然后五月份 OpenAI 也推出了同类产品\"daybreak\",效果如何没有说，但是给我的感觉挖洞这个工作是不是 Anthropic 继搞定编程这个工作后，准备要颠覆掉的下一个工作？给人感觉 Anthopic 不像其他 AI 公司开口闭口我要 AGI ，它就默默的干，一个一个领域的突破。Claude Mythos Preview 由于太牛逼 Anthropic 说在他们开发出更加牛逼的防护系统之前不对外发布，只给一些信得过的 partner 使用，有没有大佬实际用过啊？是否真的那么牛逼。\r\n\r\n4 月博文： https://red.anthropic.com/2026/mythos-preview/\r\n5 月博文： https://www.anthropic.com/research/glasswing-initial-update\r\nopenai 跟进： https://x.com/OpenAI/status/2053939702110269822", "content_rendered": "Anthopic 四月发了博文说搞了一个 Claude Mythos Preview ，挖了 500+个漏洞，前几天又更新了进展，扫描了 1000 多个开源项目发现了估计为 23019 个漏洞，某家独立的安全研究公司对其中 1752 个高危或严重级别漏洞进行了仔细评估，其中 90.6%（ 1587 个）被证实为有效漏洞，62.4%（ 1094 个）被确认为高危或严重级别。然后五月份 OpenAI 也推出了同类产品\"daybreak\",效果如何没有说，但是给我的感觉挖洞这个工作是不是 Anthropic 继搞定编程这个工作后，准备要颠覆掉的下一个工作？给人感觉 Anthopic 不像其他 AI 公司开口闭口我要 AGI ，它就默默的干，一个一个领域的突破。Claude Mythos Preview 由于太牛逼 Anthropic 说在他们开发出更加牛逼的防护系统之前不对外发布，只给一些信得过的 partner 使用，有没有大佬实际用过啊？是否真的那么牛逼。<br /><br />4 月博文： <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://red.anthropic.com/2026/mythos-preview/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://red.anthropic.com/2026/mythos-preview/</a><br />5 月博文： <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/research/glasswing-initial-update\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.anthropic.com/research/glasswing-initial-update</a><br />openai 跟进： <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://x.com/OpenAI/status/2053939702110269822\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://x.com/OpenAI/status/2053939702110269822</a>", "last_modified": 1780106530, "replies": 34, "id": 1216615}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10942, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2338, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 568461, "username": "hairenjun", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hairenjun", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/77ba760757bc9f8129bcda869fac46ff?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/77ba760757bc9f8129bcda869fac46ff?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/77ba760757bc9f8129bcda869fac46ff?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1641728878, "last_modified": 1780145491, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "levelworm", "last_touched": 1780177136, "title": "和 Gemini 聊了四个小时，现在感觉在大学去上课就是浪费时间", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216703", "created": 1780147354, "deleted": 0, "content": "其实我已经毕业于某 985 大学，上大学的时候就感觉上当受骗了，感觉就是个专科水平，啥真本事不教（当然也可能是专业问题）\r\n\r\n今天骨骼了一下各种虚拟化平台 pros and cons ， 突发奇想就顺着下面那个“Ask anything”问了下去，\r\n一聊就是 4 个小时，从主流方案到 infini band 这种追求极致效率的方案都有了大致印象，了解到了 Ansible 这种运维工具，接下来可以实践一下了，从头到尾还不收我一分钱\r\n\r\n一想到大学上的计算机课不教操作系统不教编译原理不教版本管理，就教安装 DevC++然后到链表/排序就戛然而止了（甚至不愿意教一下 malloc 和 free ，哦对了堆和栈更是没提过），还参杂大量思政内容，嗨呀真气得我直跺脚啊，浪费大把青春年华\r\n\r\n讲数据库用的 Mysql ，做那沟槽的小实验，交纸质版的试验报告； Elasticsearch 啊 Vector DB 什么的前沿技术栈都是一概没讲的，这两个我也不熟，要去找 Gemini 请教了\r\n\r\n如果你是在校大学生的话赶紧去试试 Gemini （不过能上 V2EX 的话应该也不会上大学的当吧）\r\n\r\n现在工作了要深夜还债了  我已急哭😭", "content_rendered": "<p>其实我已经毕业于某 985 大学，上大学的时候就感觉上当受骗了，感觉就是个专科水平，啥真本事不教（当然也可能是专业问题）</p>\n<p>今天骨骼了一下各种虚拟化平台 pros and cons ， 突发奇想就顺着下面那个“Ask anything”问了下去，\n一聊就是 4 个小时，从主流方案到 infini band 这种追求极致效率的方案都有了大致印象，了解到了 Ansible 这种运维工具，接下来可以实践一下了，从头到尾还不收我一分钱</p>\n<p>一想到大学上的计算机课不教操作系统不教编译原理不教版本管理，就教安装 DevC++然后到链表/排序就戛然而止了（甚至不愿意教一下 malloc 和 free ，哦对了堆和栈更是没提过），还参杂大量思政内容，嗨呀真气得我直跺脚啊，浪费大把青春年华</p>\n<p>讲数据库用的 Mysql ，做那沟槽的小实验，交纸质版的试验报告； Elasticsearch 啊 Vector DB 什么的前沿技术栈都是一概没讲的，这两个我也不熟，要去找 Gemini 请教了</p>\n<p>如果你是在校大学生的话赶紧去试试 Gemini （不过能上 V2EX 的话应该也不会上大学的当吧）</p>\n<p>现在工作了要深夜还债了  我已急哭😭</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780147354, "replies": 34, "id": 1216703}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 238862, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4490, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 1953, "username": "jumkey", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jumkey", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9e43192b4eb715af248dbdef6a9c043d?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9e43192b4eb715af248dbdef6a9c043d?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9e43192b4eb715af248dbdef6a9c043d?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1285736654, "last_modified": 1770263778, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "ysc3839", "last_touched": 1780171524, "title": "各位大佬们，固态硬盘到底分不分区？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216669", "created": 1780128470, "deleted": 0, "content": "记得之前看到过，有人说固态盘不建议分区，到底要不要分区？分区影响整体寿命吗？还是说不分区使用更好？", "content_rendered": "<p>记得之前看到过，有人说固态盘不建议分区，到底要不要分区？分区影响整体寿命吗？还是说不分区使用更好？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780128470, "replies": 32, "id": 1216669}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1649080598", "name": "macos", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1649080598", "title": "macOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos", "topics": 23852, "footer": "<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598", "stars": 5476, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 194581, "username": "leon912", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/leon912", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a4c5/66be/194581_mini.png?m=1612418210", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a4c5/66be/194581_normal.png?m=1612418210", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a4c5/66be/194581_large.png?m=1612418210", "created": 1475594181, "last_modified": 1612418210, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "lloyds", "last_touched": 1780172808, "title": "HP 打印机没有 mac 驱动怎么办？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216672", "created": 1780128928, "deleted": 0, "content": "买了个 hp 的打印机，比较便宜的那种。hp 105w 激光打印机。\r\n官网没有 mac 系统的驱动，windows 倒是正常。\r\n苹果官网好像也没找到这种打印机的解决方案。\r\n不知道大家有没有过类似的经验，该怎么处理？", "content_rendered": "<p>买了个 hp 的打印机，比较便宜的那种。hp 105w 激光打印机。\n官网没有 mac 系统的驱动，windows 倒是正常。\n苹果官网好像也没找到这种打印机的解决方案。\n不知道大家有没有过类似的经验，该怎么处理？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780128928, "replies": 28, "id": 1216672}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1754172750", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1754172750", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 12862, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1754172750", "stars": 6205, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 39, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 624972, "username": "YaNanGe", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/YaNanGe", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e409/2597/624972_mini.png?m=1730697636", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e409/2597/624972_normal.png?m=1730697636", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e409/2597/624972_large.png?m=1730697636", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e409/2597/624972_xlarge.png?m=1730697636", "created": 1681959737, "last_modified": 1730697636, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "w568w", "last_touched": 1780165643, "title": "有没有大佬知道如何获取安卓唯一标识", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216634", "created": 1780110683, "deleted": 0, "content": "如题，公司自己内部使用的 APP ，不需要上架商店，扫码安装。\r\n\r\n系统为 11 、12 。设备需要经常刷机。\r\n\r\n在不 root ，不通过电脑单独开启某权限的情况下如何获取不会改变的唯一编码？", "content_rendered": "如题，公司自己内部使用的 APP ，不需要上架商店，扫码安装。<br /><br />系统为 11 、12 。设备需要经常刷机。<br /><br />在不 root ，不通过电脑单独开启某权限的情况下如何获取不会改变的唯一编码？", "last_modified": 1780130668, "replies": 25, "id": 1216634}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_large.png?m=1751736785", "name": "openai", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_normal.png?m=1751736785", "title": "OpenAI", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/openai", "topics": 3946, "footer": "", "header": "关于 OpenAI 旗下产品 GPT，DALL·E，和 ChatGPT 的讨论。请不要在 V2EX 的回复中粘贴复制来自 AI 生成的文本。", "title_alternative": "OpenAI", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fd2c/5e46/1135_mini.png?m=1751736785", "stars": 3105, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1135, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 76854, "username": "wuruxu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wuruxu", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "wuruxu", "btc": "", "location": "杭州", "tagline": "佛眼之下 👁️‍🗨️ 俱是微尘", "bio": "Oldman", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0c1d/51f3/76854_mini.png?m=1779115433", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0c1d/51f3/76854_normal.png?m=1779115433", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0c1d/51f3/76854_large.png?m=1779115433", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0c1d/51f3/76854_xlarge.png?m=1779115433", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0c1d/51f3/76854_xxlarge.png?m=1779115433", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0c1d/51f3/76854_xxxlarge.png?m=1779115433", "created": 1413100347, "last_modified": 1779115433, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "anotherbot", "last_touched": 1780152792, "title": "给大二的小孩买了 GPT Go", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216664", "created": 1780125304, "deleted": 0, "content": "前几天抱怨免费的不够用         \r\n今天给买了 Go 套餐，感觉用来完成学校的事情 应该足够了", "content_rendered": "<p>前几天抱怨免费的不够用<br/>\n今天给买了 Go 套餐，感觉用来完成学校的事情 应该足够了</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780125304, "replies": 25, "id": 1216664}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23470, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3687, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 526487, "username": "Carver9527", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Carver9527", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/49d6fcc3fd0f0bbdb22068e4ca8c4822?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/49d6fcc3fd0f0bbdb22068e4ca8c4822?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/49d6fcc3fd0f0bbdb22068e4ca8c4822?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1609568610, "last_modified": 1609568610, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "panzhc", "last_touched": 1780156161, "title": "开发转运维，是否是一条不归路", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216610", "created": 1780104963, "deleted": 0, "content": "背景：二本 Go 开发，7 年经验，今年 4 月初拿到礼包，没到能够躺平的水平。\r\n\r\n开始投简历，准备找下一份工作。中间经过一些波折，最终收获了一份运维开发的 offer 。期间因为一直没有合适的机会，整个人都焦虑了。\r\n\r\n入职几天，发现主要是做运维的工作，而且需要值班，强度一下被拉高了，怀疑自己是不是走上了一条不归路。", "content_rendered": "<p>背景：二本 Go 开发，7 年经验，今年 4 月初拿到礼包，没到能够躺平的水平。</p>\n<p>开始投简历，准备找下一份工作。中间经过一些波折，最终收获了一份运维开发的 offer 。期间因为一直没有合适的机会，整个人都焦虑了。</p>\n<p>入职几天，发现主要是做运维的工作，而且需要值班，强度一下被拉高了，怀疑自己是不是走上了一条不归路。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780106507, "replies": 23, "id": 1216610}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71301, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9694, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 736843, "username": "hubianluanma", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hubianluanma", "website": "https://hubianluanma.com", "twitter": "huhailong1121", "psn": "", "github": "hubianluanma", "btc": "", "location": "北京", "tagline": "胡编乱码", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a2f/2db0/736843_mini.png?m=1750909443", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a2f/2db0/736843_normal.png?m=1750909443", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a2f/2db0/736843_large.png?m=1750909443", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a2f/2db0/736843_xlarge.png?m=1750909443", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a2f/2db0/736843_xxlarge.png?m=1750909443", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3a2f/2db0/736843_xxxlarge.png?m=1750909443", "created": 1740547572, "last_modified": 1750909443, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "yuhaofe", "last_touched": 1780149525, "title": "Kimi Code 用起来感觉还行，就是很容易达到限额", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216645", "created": 1780115482, "deleted": 0, "content": "公司用的是 Cursor ，平时工作都会选择 Opus4.6 处理，自己平时订阅了 MiniMax 和 Kimi Code 俩个 49 元档的计划。使用 MiniMax 主要是给 Hermes Agent 用的，因为除了语言大模型还支持图片、语音生成、歌曲/歌词生成，还有翻唱，感觉作为日常助手很不错，Kimi Code 的话是因为在使用了一段时间 Claude Code + MiniMax-M2.7 进行编码任务后发现它对上下文理解和代码理解能力确实不如 Kimi 。尤其最近在使用 playwright-mcp 结合 AI 去做自动化测试发现，一些操作，使用 Cursor 中的高级模型或者使用 Kimi ，这些操作都能自己顺利完成，而使用 MiniMax 的话老是说不能操作，需要人工复验。\r\n\r\n我觉得抛开国外的不谈，现在 Kimi Code 已经算不错的了。", "content_rendered": "<p>公司用的是 Cursor ，平时工作都会选择 Opus4.6 处理，自己平时订阅了 MiniMax 和 Kimi Code 俩个 49 元档的计划。使用 MiniMax 主要是给 Hermes Agent 用的，因为除了语言大模型还支持图片、语音生成、歌曲/歌词生成，还有翻唱，感觉作为日常助手很不错，Kimi Code 的话是因为在使用了一段时间 Claude Code + MiniMax-M2.7 进行编码任务后发现它对上下文理解和代码理解能力确实不如 Kimi 。尤其最近在使用 playwright-mcp 结合 AI 去做自动化测试发现，一些操作，使用 Cursor 中的高级模型或者使用 Kimi ，这些操作都能自己顺利完成，而使用 MiniMax 的话老是说不能操作，需要人工复验。</p>\n<p>我觉得抛开国外的不谈，现在 Kimi Code 已经算不错的了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1780115482, "replies": 23, "id": 1216645}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_large.png?m=1648291973", "name": "reading", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_normal.png?m=1648291973", "title": "阅读", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/reading", "topics": 816, "footer": "", "header": "少上网，多读书", "title_alternative": "Reading", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_mini.png?m=1648291973", "stars": 1718, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 111, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 660849, "username": "chaoziCoder", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/chaoziCoder", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/770d3e6108053578d11ab5d4d0b96d5f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/770d3e6108053578d11ab5d4d0b96d5f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/770d3e6108053578d11ab5d4d0b96d5f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1699277345, "last_modified": 1780112530, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "unusualcat", "last_touched": 1780154896, "title": "穿越，带着 Codex 回到互联网的黄金时代", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1216640", "created": 1780112608, "deleted": 0, "content": "![带着 Codex 回到互联网黄金期]( https://ship-image.chaozi.work/uploads/1780112453498-WoJp6u34CphDyyfy2f3Cz.webp)", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"带着 Codex 回到互联网黄金期\" class=\"embedded_image\" load